Globacom has introduced the Glo LTE Mifi device with subscribers getting 30 gigabytes (gb) of data on purchase. In a statement, the company said the new device gives customers value for money and a pleasant browsing experience on its Glo 4G LTE network. “This offer gives subscribers free 30gb data (valid for 30 days) upon purchase of a MiFi. They will also get additional 5gb data every time they purchase a data plan,” it stated. “The offer will last for the next six months,” it said.